{"type":"message","id":"794501e8","parentId":"f3e52228","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:15:40.243Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger wants me to update the skill documentation. Let me update the SKILL.md file with the correct JSON format.","thinkingSignature":"6f2d7eba36eed31d451a74703a8f42dd4ae97e09ae5d748571d9f11765c280b5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_23ym7t4wur68_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"### 步骤2：配置OpenClaw多Agent\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"it-engineer\",\n        \"name\": \"IT工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\it-engineer\",\n        \"tools\": {\n          \"profile\": \"full\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"web-developer\",\n        \"name\": \"网站开发工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\web-developer\",\n        \"tools\": {\n          \"profile\": \"full\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"pv-engineer\",\n        \"name\": \"光伏系统开发工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\pv-engineer\",\n        \"tools\": {\n          \"profile\": \"full\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"pv-engineer\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_xxx1\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"xxx1\",\n          \"botName\": \"光伏系统开发工程师\"\n        },\n        \"web-developer\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_xxx2\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"xxx2\",\n          \"botName\": \"网站开发工程师\"\n        },\n        \"it-engineer\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_xxx3\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"xxx3\",\n          \"botName\": \"IT工程师\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"dmPolicy\": \"pairing\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**注意**：\n- 每个 Bot 需要独立的飞书应用（不同的 App ID 和 App Secret）\n- `dmPolicy: \"pairing\"` 表示私聊时需要配对\n- `accounts` 下的 key（如 `pv-engineer`）需与 `agents.list` 中的 `id` 对应","oldText":"### 步骤2：配置OpenClaw多Agent\n\n编辑 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"it-engineer\",\n        \"identity\": \"🔧 IT工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\it-engineer\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"web-developer\",\n        \"identity\": \"🌐 网站开发工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\web-developer\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"pv-engineer\",\n        \"identity\": \"☀️ 光储系统工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\pv-engineer\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"cli_a93e197da0389bc7\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"KHIFVauyQQZ2QBw3NATLmfWOZB6Y3gro\",\n      \"mentionBotId\": \"ou_f75fa2e77e5d7651f90be461a4fb2104\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\single-group-multi-bot\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":782,"cacheRead":84547,"cacheWrite":2587,"totalTokens":87952,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0009383999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00253641,"cacheWrite":0.00031044,"total":0.0037960499999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773587704218}}
