\": {\n+ 98           \"appId\": \"cli_xxx1\",\n+ 99           \"appSecret\": \"xxx1\",\n+100           \"botName\": \"光伏系统开发工程师\"\n+101         },\n+102         \"web-developer\": {\n+103           \"appId\": \"cli_xxx2\",\n+104           \"appSecret\": \"xxx2\",\n+105           \"botName\": \"网站开发工程师\"\n+106         },\n+107         \"it-engineer\": {\n+108           \"appId\": \"cli_xxx3\",\n+109           \"appSecret\": \"xxx3\",\n+110           \"botName\": \"IT工程师\"\n+111         }\n+112       },\n+113       \"dmPolicy\": \"pairing\"\n  89     }\n  90   }\n  91 }\n  92 ```\n  93 \n+119 **注意**：\n+120 - 每个 Bot 需要独立的飞书应用（不同的 App ID 和 App Secret）\n+121 - `dmPolicy: \"pairing\"` 表示私聊时需要配对\n+122 - `accounts` 下的 key（如 `pv-engineer`）需与 `agents.list` 中的 `id` 对应\n+123 \n  94 ### 步骤3：创建Agent工作空间\n  95 \n  96 为每个Agent创建独立的工作空间目录：\n  97 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":69},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773587740251}}
{"type":"message","id":"7c23c149","parentId":"981351d0","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:15:50.309Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also update the distributed deployment example section with the correct format.","thinkingSignature":"a0512985b10d5cc0da788019c208f8134134f4190916e7e46eaf3e4f75f3ad77"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_wv64qztiqwk4_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"3. **配置各服务器OpenClaw**\n```json\n// 服务器A (IT工程师)\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"it-engineer\",\n      \"name\": \"IT工程师\",\n      \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\it-engineer\",\n      \"tools\": { \"profile\": \"full\" }\n    }]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"it-engineer\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_a\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"xxx_a\",\n          \"botName\": \"IT工程师\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 服务器B (网站开发)\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"web-developer\",\n      \"name\": \"网站开发工程师\",\n      \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\web-developer\",\n      \"tools\": { \"profile\": \"full\" }\n    }]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"web-developer\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_b\", \n          \"appSecret\": \"xxx_b\",\n          \"botName\": \"网站开发工程师\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```","oldText":"3. **配置各服务器OpenClaw**\n```json\n// 服务器A (IT工程师)\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"it-engineer\",\n      \"identity\": \"🔧 IT工程师\",\n      \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\it-engineer\"\n    }]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_a\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"xxx_a\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n\n// 服务器B (网站开发)\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [{\n      \"id\": \"web-developer\",\n      \"identity\": \"🌐 网站开发工程师\",\n      \"workspace\": \"~\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\web-developer\"\n    }]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"cli_xxx_b\", \n      \"appSecret\": \"xxx_b\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\single-group-multi-bot\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":70593,"output":587,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88579,"cost":{"input":0.0211779,"output":0.0007044,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02240427}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773587740254}}
