{"type":"message","id":"4bf77e7a","parentId":"93a69ff7","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:15:56.126Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me also add a note about the bot response mechanism being based on @ mentions rather than mentionBotId.","thinkingSignature":"b86670237f19c6b5e59b46658f62082d2de927440f38ecb413ca895fa87effde"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_b4v08numxz5r_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"## 💡 使用技巧\n\n### 1. Bot响应机制\n\n群聊中通过 @提及 某个 Bot 来触发响应。例如：\n- @光伏系统开发工程师 → pv-engineer 处理\n- @网站开发工程师 → web-developer 处理\n- @IT工程师 → it-engineer 处理\n\n系统会根据消息中 @ 的用户自动路由到对应的 Agent。","oldText":"## 💡 使用技巧\n\n### 1. Bot响应机制\n\n默认配置下，只有被@的Bot会响应。如需自动回复，修改`mentionBotId`配置。","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\single-group-multi-bot\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":71220,"output":196,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88815,"cost":{"input":0.021366,"output":0.0002352,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02212317}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773587750331}}
