{"type":"message","id":"0a3f3bf3","parentId":"0bcd6464","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:16:12.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me just verify the changes I've made so far are good and inform the user.","thinkingSignature":"d1a19daecfdddf55ce53667be423483f6676a8a60de4a30dcb69b06c77bb4c51"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **技能文档已更新！**\n\n更新内容：\n1. ✅ JSON 配置格式改为正确的 `accounts` 结构\n2. ✅ 添加了 `dmPolicy: \"pairing\"` 说明\n3. ✅ 移除了不存在的 `mentionBotId` 配置\n4. ✅ 更新了分布式部署的示例配置\n5. ✅ 优化了 Bot 响应机制说明\n6. ✅ 添加了 skills 目录说明\n\n文档现在与实际配置格式一致了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":72053,"output":117,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":89569,"cost":{"input":0.0216159,"output":0.0001404,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02227827}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773587768150}}
