{"type":"message","id":"495da69c","parentId":"a65cea9e","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:26:32.526Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger wants me to fix the issues in the multi-agent-feishu-deployment skill. Let me make the necessary edits to fix the problems:\n\n1. JSON format - update to use `accounts` instead of `appId`/`appSecret` directly and `multiAppSupport`\n2. identity -> name\n3. Path format - change Linux paths to Windows paths\n4. workspace directory - change `workspaces/admin` to `workspace/agents/`\n\nThis is a large file, so I'll need to make multiple edits. Let me start with the main SKILL.md file.","thinkingSignature":"9d593de412e47dc184bb96f0a2b31742dba006eaa5ce05811c07477cc58da2e6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c5ayn759bupg_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"#### 方法B：手动配置OpenClaw\n```json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"admin-assistant\",\n        \"name\": \"行政专员\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\admin-assistant\",\n        \"tools\": { \"profile\": \"full\" }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"it-engineer\",\n        \"name\": \"IT工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\it-engineer\",\n        \"tools\": { \"profile\": \"full\" }\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"financial-expert\",\n        \"name\": \"金融专家\",\n        \"workspace\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\xxx\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\agents\\\\financial-expert\",\n        \"tools\": { \"profile\": \"full\" }\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"admin-assistant\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_work_app_id\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"work_app_secret\",\n          \"botName\": \"行政专员\"\n        },\n        \"it-engineer\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_it_app_id\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"it_app_secret\",\n          \"botName\": \"IT工程师\"\n        },\n        \"financial-expert\": {\n          \"appId\": \"cli_finance_app_id\",\n          \"appSecret\": \"finance_app_secret\",\n          \"botName\": \"金融专家\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"dmPolicy\": \"pairing\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```","oldText":"#### 方法B：手动配置OpenClaw\n```json\n// /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n{\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"main\",\n        \"identity\": \"👔 CEO\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"admin-assistant\",\n        \"identity\": \"📋 行政专员\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/admin\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"it-engineer\",\n        \"identity\": \"🔧 IT工程师\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/it\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"id\": \"financial-expert\",\n        \"identity\": \"💰 金融专家\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/finance\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"multiAppSupport\": {\n        \"enabled\": true,\n        \"apps\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"work\",\n            \"appId\": \"cli_work_app_id\",\n            \"appSecret\": \"work_app_secret\",\n            \"agent\": \"admin-assistant\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"it\",\n            \"appId\": \"cli_it_app_id\",\n            \"appSecret\": \"it_app_secret\",\n            \"agent\": \"it-engineer\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"finance\",\n            \"appId\": \"cli_finance_app_id\",\n            \"appSecret\": \"finance_app_secret\",\n            \"agent\": \"financial-expert\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":883,"cacheRead":94726,"cacheWrite":6376,"totalTokens":102021,"cost":{"i