{"type":"message","id":"86f1ba43","parentId":"10752b51","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:26:57.617Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also fix the other parts that use Linux paths. Let me check for more Linux paths in the document.","thinkingSignature":"1368b46981e3f610add9af9c8e29987be20572681554bb350510f9ca4c51b1b6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_nq2y3it5qzh5_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"### 步骤4：部署配置\n\n#### 方法A：使用自动化部署脚本\n```bash\n# 配置参数\nWORK_PORT=18790\nPERSONAL_PORT=18791\nPROJECT_PORT=18792\n\n# 创建实例目录\nmkdir -p C:\\openclaw-multi\\work\nmkdir -p C:\\openclaw-multi\\personal\nmkdir -p C:\\openclaw-multi\\project\n\n# 部署完成\necho \"部署完成！\"\n```\n\n#### 方法B：手动配置OpenClaw\n参考上方 JSON 配置示例","oldText":"### 步骤4：部署配置\n\n#### 方法A：使用自动化部署脚本\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# setup-multi-agent-feishu.sh\n\n# 配置参数\nWORK_PORT=18790\nPERSONAL_PORT=18791\nPROJECT_PORT=18792\n\n# 创建实例目录\nmkdir -p /root/.openclaw-multi/{work,personal,project}\n\n# 复制基础配置\nfor instance in work personal project; do\n  cp -r /root/.openclaw/* /root/.openclaw-multi/$instance/\ndone\n\n# 配置工作实例\ncat > /root/.openclaw-multi/work/openclaw.json << EOF\n{\n  \"gateway\": {\n    \"port\": $WORK_PORT\n  },\n  \"channels\": {\n    \"feishu\": {\n      \"appId\": \"$WORK_APP_ID\",\n      \"appSecret\": \"$WORK_APP_SECRET\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"agents\": {\n    \"list\": [\n      {\n        \"id\": \"admin-assistant\",\n        \"workspace\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspaces/admin\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\nEOF\n\n# 更多配置...\necho \"部署完成！\"\n```","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":85807,"output":440,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103646,"cost":{"input":0.0257421,"output":0.0005279999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02679207}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773588410302}}
