{"type":"message","id":"ee444061","parentId":"e035c5fb","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:27:07.107Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me fix more Linux paths in the rest of the document. Let me search and replace more occurrences.","thinkingSignature":"86fb34a26a16232e08c6fc1afaba5df80a1ab2f927ccb526af0495832203a531"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_brmkowhx0o66_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"#### 创建路由中间件\n```javascript\n// C:\\openclaw-multi\\feishu-router.js\nconst express = require('express');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\n\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json());\n\n// 应用映射配置\nconst APP_MAPPING = {\n  'cli_work_app_id': {\n    name: 'work',\n    agent: 'admin-assistant',\n    secret: 'work_app_secret',\n    endpoint: 'http://127.0.0.1:18790/api/message'\n  },\n  'cli_it_app_id': {\n    name: 'it',\n    agent: 'it-engineer',\n    secret: 'it_app_secret',\n    endpoint: 'http://127.0.0.1:18791/api/message'\n  },\n  'cli_finance_app_id': {\n    name: 'finance',\n    agent: 'financial-expert',\n    secret: 'finance_app_secret',\n    endpoint: 'http://127.0.0.1:18792/api/message'\n  }\n};","oldText":"#### 创建路由中间件\n```javascript\n// /root/.openclaw-multi/feishu-router.js\nconst express = require('express');\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\n\nconst app = express();\napp.use(express.json());\n\n// 应用映射配置\nconst APP_MAPPING = {\n  'cli_work_app_id': {\n    name: 'work',\n    agent: 'admin-assistant',\n    secret: 'work_app_secret',\n    endpoint: 'http://127.0.0.1:18790/api/message'\n  },\n  'cli_it_app_id': {\n    name: 'it',\n    agent: 'it-engineer',\n    secret: 'it_app_secret',\n    endpoint: 'http://127.0.0.1:18791/api/message'\n  },\n  'cli_finance_app_id': {\n    name: 'finance',\n    agent: 'financial-expert',\n    secret: 'finance_app_secret',\n    endpoint: 'http://127.0.0.1:18792/api/message'\n  }\n};","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":86289,"output":516,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104204,"cost":{"input":0.0258867,"output":0.0006192,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02702787}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773588417630}}
{"type":"message","id":"a68c995b","parentId":"ee444061","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:27:07.134Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_brmkowhx0o66_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 170 ### 步骤5：消息路由配置\n 171 \n 172 #### 创建路由中间件\n 173 ```javascript\n-174 // /root/.openclaw-multi/feishu-router.js\n+174 // C:\\openclaw-multi\\feishu-router.js\n 175 const express = require('express');\n 176 const crypto = require('crypto');\n 177 \n 178 const app = express();\n     ...","firstChangedLine":174},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773588427123}}
{"type":"message","id":"73053f7f","parentId":"a68c995b","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:27:41.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me continue fixing more Linux paths. There are many more in the troubleshooting and other sections.","thinkingSignature":"789c82c67e8aca9ed250a260ad7d3477a56f7781815f323f496d0c8d0f5a1a24"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_8nkog59zw4tp_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"#### 1. Agent无法启动\n**症状**: Agent未运行\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 检查Agent配置\nopenclaw agents describe admin-assistant\n\n# 重新创建Agent\nopenclaw agents add admin-assistant --workspace C:\\Users\\xxx\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\admin-assistant\n```\n\n#### 2. 飞书消息路由失败\n**症状**: 消息没有到达对应Agent\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 检查路由中间件日志\n# 日志路径: C:\\openclaw-multi\\logs\\router.log\n\n# 验证飞书应用配置\n# 访问飞书开放平台验证应用凭证\n\n# 测试路由逻辑\nnode C:\\openclaw-multi\\test-router.js\n```\n\n#### 3. 性能问题\n**症状**: 响应延迟高，资源使用率高\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 调整并发设置\nopenclaw config set gateway.maxConcurrentSessions 5\n\n# 清理旧会话\nopenclaw sessions cleanup --older-than 24h\n```\n\n#### 4. 权限问题\n**症状**: Agent无法访问所需资源\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 检查文件权限\ndir C:\\Users\\xxx\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\admin-assistant\\\n\n# 检查飞书应用权限\nopenclaw feishu_app_scopes\n```","oldText":"#### 1. Agent无法启动\n**症状**: `openclaw agents list` 显示Agent未运行\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 检查Agent配置\nopenclaw agents describe admin-assistant\n\n# 查看详细错误\ntail -100 /root/.openclaw/agents/admin-assistant/agent/error.log\n\n# 重新创建Agent\nopenclaw agents add admin-assistant --workspace /root/.openclaw/workspaces/admin\n```\n\n#### 2. 飞书消息路由失败\n**症状**: 消息没有到达对应Agent\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 检查路由中间件日志\ntail -f /var/log/feishu-router.log\n\n# 验证飞书应用配置\ncurl -X POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/app_access_token/internal/ \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"app_id\":\"cli_xxx\",\"app_secret\":\"xxx\"}'\n\n# 测试路由逻辑\nnode /root/.openclaw-multi/test-router.js\n```\n\n#### 3. 性能问题\n**症状**: 响应延迟高，资源使用率高\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 优化资源配置\nsystemctl edit openclaw-work\n# 添加: MemoryLimit=1G CPUQuota=50%\n\n# 调整并发设置\nopenclaw config set gateway.maxConcurrentSessions 5\n\n# 清理旧会话\nopenclaw sessions cleanup --older-than 24h\n```\n\n#### 4. 权限问题\n**症状**: Agent无法访问所需资源\n**解决**:\n```bash\n# 检查文件权限\nls -la /root/.openclaw/workspaces/admin/\n\n# 检查飞书应用权限\nopenclaw feishu_app_scopes\n\n# 重新授权\n# 访问飞书开放平台，重新授权所需权限\n```","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":86847,"output":743,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104989,"cost":{"input":0.0260541,"output":0.0008916,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02746767}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773588427134}}
{"type":"message","id":"9119cf16","parentId":"73053f7f","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:27:41.155Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_8nkog59zw4tp_1","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced text in C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md."}],"details":{"diff":"     ...\n 330 \n 331 ### 常见问题及解决方案\n 332 \n 333 #### 1. Agent无法启动\n-334 **症状**: `openclaw agents list` 显示Agent未运行\n+334 **症状**: Agent未运行\n 335 **解决**:\n 336 ```bash\n 337 # 检查Agent配置\n 338 openclaw agents describe admin-assistant\n 339 \n-340 # 查看详细错误\n-341 tail -100 /root/.openclaw/agents/admin-assistant/agent/error.log\n-342 \n 343 # 重新创建Agent\n-344 openclaw agents add admin-assistant --workspace /root/.openclaw/workspaces/admin\n+341 openclaw agents add admin-assistant --workspace C:\\Users\\xxx\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\admin-assistant\n 345 ```\n 346 \n 347 #### 2. 飞书消息路由失败\n 348 **症状**: 消息没有到达对应Agent\n 349 **解决**:\n 350 ```bash\n 351 # 检查路由中间件日志\n-352 tail -f /var/log/feishu-router.log\n+349 # 日志路径: C:\\openclaw-multi\\logs\\router.log\n 353 \n 354 # 验证飞书应用配置\n-355 curl -X POST https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/auth/v3/app_access_token/internal/ \\\n-356   -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n-357   -d '{\"app_id\":\"cli_xxx\",\"app_secret\":\"xxx\"}'\n+352 # 访问飞书开放平台验证应用凭证\n 358 \n 359 # 测试路由逻辑\n-360 node /root/.openclaw-multi/test-router.js\n+355 node C:\\openclaw-multi\\test-router.js\n 361 ```\n 362 \n 363 #### 3. 性能问题\n 364 **症状**: 响应延迟高，资源使用率高\n 365 **解决**:\n 366 ```bash\n-367 # 优化资源配置\n-368 systemctl edit openclaw-work\n-369 # 添加: MemoryLimit=1G CPUQuota=50%\n-370 \n 371 # 调整并发设置\n 372 openclaw config set gateway.maxConcurrentSessions 5\n 373 \n 374 # 清理旧会话\n 375 openclaw sessions cleanup --older-than 24h\n 376 ```\n 377 \n 378 #### 4. 权限问题\n 379 **症状**: Agent无法访问所需资源\n 380 **解决**:\n 381 ```bash\n 382 # 检查文件权限\n-383 ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspaces/admin/\n+374 dir C:\\Users\\xxx\\.openclaw\\workspace\\agents\\admin-assistant\\\n 384 \n 385 # 检查飞书应用权限\n 386 openclaw feishu_app_scopes\n-387 \n-388 # 重新授权\n-389 # 访问飞书开放平台，重新授权所需权限\n 390 ```\n 391 \n 392 ## 📈 监控告警\n 393 \n     ...","firstChangedLine":334},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773588461149}}
{"type":"message","id":"519269ef","parentId":"9119cf16","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:27:49.053Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me fix the monitoring section which also has Linux paths.","thinkingSignature":"6118b24749da56a5776923581d3f9dd9b94b33c7eb2b902f9c760f9f2bc7ff8d"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o2o4c2kefrrq_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"## 📈 监控告警\n\n### 监控指标\n```bash\n# 检查实例状态\n# Windows PowerShell\nTest-NetConnection -ComputerName localhost -Port 18790\n\n# 检查资源使用\n# Windows 任务管理器或 PowerShell\nGet-Process node | Select-Object Name, CPU, WorkingSet64\n```","oldText":"## 📈 监控告警\n\n### 监控指标\n```bash\n# 创建监控脚本\ncat > /root/.openclaw-multi/monitor.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n\n# 检查实例状态\ncheck_instance() {\n  local instance=$1\n  local port=$2\n  \n  if curl -s http://127.0.0.1:$port/health >/dev/null; then\n    echo \"✅ $instance (端口:$port) 正常\"\n  else\n    echo \"❌ $instance (端口:$port) 异常\"\n    # 发送告警\n    send_alert \"$instance 服务异常\"\n  fi\n}\n\n# 检查所有实例\ncheck_instance \"work\" 18790\ncheck_instance \"it\" 18791\ncheck_instance \"finance\" 18792\n\n# 检查资源使用\ncheck_resources() {\n  local memory=$(free -m | awk '/^Mem:/{print $3}')\n  local max_memory=4096 # 4GB\n  \n  if [ $memory -gt $max_memory ]; then\n    echo \"⚠️  内存使用过高: ${memory}MB\"\n    send_alert \"系统内存使用过高\"\n  fi\n}\nEOF\nchmod +x /root/.openclaw-multi/monitor.sh\n```","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":87632,"output":418,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":105449,"cost":{"input":0.0262896,"output":0.0005015999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02731317}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773588461154}}
