{"type":"message","id":"0ce475a5","parentId":"6ad861b7","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:27:59.023Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me fix the backup section which also has Linux paths.","thinkingSignature":"daf731ea131b76f19153b19cbfdccb6a9673c58916f5deb47f461dd1485a0bd6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6kw2m335f3yk_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"newText":"## 🔄 备份恢复\n\n### 备份策略\n```bash\n# 备份配置\n# 复制以下目录到备份位置:\n# - C:\\Users\\xxx\\.openclaw\\\n# - C:\\openclaw-multi\\\n\n# 使用 Windows 备份命令\nCopy-Item -Recurse C:\\Users\\xxx\\.openclaw D:\\backup\\openclaw-$((Get-Date).ToString('yyyyMMdd'))\n```\n\n### 恢复流程\n```bash\n# 恢复配置\n# 1. 停止所有服务\nopenclaw gateway stop\n\n# 2. 恢复配置\nCopy-Item -Recurse D:\\backup\\openclaw-xxx\\* C:\\Users\\xxx\\.openclaw\\\n\n# 3. 重启服务\nopenclaw gateway start\n\necho \"恢复完成\"\n```","oldText":"## 🔄 备份恢复\n\n### 备份策略\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# backup-multi-agent.sh\n\nBACKUP_DIR=\"/backup/openclaw-multi\"\nDATE=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)\n\n# 创建备份目录\nmkdir -p $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE\n\n# 备份配置\ncp -r /root/.openclaw-multi/* $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE/\ncp /etc/systemd/system/openclaw-*.service $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE/\n\n# 备份Agent数据\nfor workspace in admin it finance; do\n  tar -czf $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE/workspace-$workspace.tar.gz /root/.openclaw/workspaces/$workspace/\ndone\n\n# 备份数据库（如果有）\n# mysqldump -u root -p openclaw > $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE/database.sql\n\necho \"备份完成: $BACKUP_DIR/$DATE\"\n```\n\n### 恢复流程\n```bash\n#!/bin/bash\n# restore-multi-agent.sh\n\nBACKUP_DATE=\"20260306_120000\"\nBACKUP_DIR=\"/backup/openclaw-multi/$BACKUP_DATE\"\n\n# 停止所有服务\nsystemctl stop openclaw-work openclaw-it openclaw-finance\n\n# 恢复配置\ncp -r $BACKUP_DIR/* /root/.openclaw-multi/\ncp $BACKUP_DIR/openclaw-*.service /etc/systemd/system/\n\n# 恢复Agent数据\nfor workspace in admin it finance; do\n  tar -xzf $BACKUP_DIR/workspace-$workspace.tar.gz -C /\ndone\n\n# 重新加载服务\nsystemctl daemon-reload\nsystemctl start openclaw-work openclaw-it openclaw-finance\n\necho \"恢复完成\"\n```","path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":88092,"output":603,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106094,"cost":{"input":0.0264276,"output":0.0007235999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.02767317}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773588469076}}
