{"type":"message","id":"b26a492a","parentId":"fca6c5d0","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:30:47.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"setup.sh 文件也需要修复。这是一个 bash 脚本，但在 Windows 上可能不需要了。不过还是修复它以保持一致性。","thinkingSignature":"5259d49db9dfefbbcbb066b7ae2ae7f982f1ced3438c7f85f17e3411cc21a9fb"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pmwoks5wtrk7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":100,"path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\multi-agent-feishu-deployment\\setup.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":94051,"output":79,"cacheRead":17399,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111529,"cost":{"input":0.0282153,"output":0.0000948,"cacheRead":0.00052197,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.028832069999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773588642265}}
{"type":"message","id":"935fde6e","parentId":"b26a492a","timestamp":"2026-03-15T15:30:47.306Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_pmwoks5wtrk7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n\n# 多Agent多飞书应用部署脚本\n# 基于行政专员和IT工程师的部署经验\n\nset -e\n\necho \"🚀 开始部署多Agent多飞书应用系统\"\necho \"======================================\"\n\n# 颜色定义\nRED='\\033[0;31m'\nGREEN='\\033[0;32m'\nYELLOW='\\033[1;33m'\nNC='\\033[0m' # No Color\n\n# 日志函数\nlog_info() {\n    echo -e \"${GREEN}[INFO]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\nlog_warn() {\n    echo -e \"${YELLOW}[WARN]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\nlog_error() {\n    echo -e \"${RED}[ERROR]${NC} $1\"\n}\n\n# 检查依赖\ncheck_dependencies() {\n    log_info \"检查系统依赖...\"\n    \n    # 检查OpenClaw\n    if command -v openclaw &> /dev/null; then\n        log_info \"✅ OpenClaw 已安装\"\n    else\n        log_error \"❌ OpenClaw 未安装，请先安装OpenClaw\"\n        exit 1\n    fi\n    \n    # 检查Node.js\n    if command -v node &> /dev/null; then\n        log_info \"✅ Node.js 已安装\"\n    else\n        log_warn \"⚠️  Node.js 未安装，部分功能可能受限\"\n    fi\n    \n    # 检查systemd\n    if systemctl --version &> /dev/null; then\n        log_info \"✅ systemd 可用\"\n    else\n        log_warn \"⚠️  systemd 不可用，将使用其他方式管理服务\"\n    fi\n}\n\n# 创建目录结构\ncreate_directories() {\n    log_info \"创建目录结构...\"\n    \n    # 主目录\n    mkdir -p /root/.openclaw-multi\n    mkdir -p /root/.openclaw-multi/{scripts,configs,backups,logs}\n    \n    # Agent工作空间\n    mkdir -p /root/.openclaw/workspaces/{admin,it,finance,project,personal}\n    \n    # 实例目录\n    mkdir -p /root/.openclaw-multi/instances/{work,it,finance}\n    \n    log_info \"✅ 目录结构创建完成\"\n}\n\n# 配置Agent身份\nsetup_agent_identities() {\n    log_info \"配置Agent身份...\"\n    \n    # 行政专员\n    cat > /root/.openclaw/workspaces/admin/IDENTITY.md << 'EOF'\n# 行政专员 Agent\n\n- **名称**: 行政专员\n- **角色**: 行政事务处理专家\n- **专长**: 文档管理、日程安排、会议协调\n- **服务对象**: 工作版飞书应用用户\n\n## 核心职责\n1. 文档处理与归档\n2. 会议安排与纪要\n3. 日程管理与提醒\n4. 行政协调与沟通\n5. 数据整理与报告\nEOF\n    log_info \"✅ 行政专员身份配置完成\"\n    \n    # IT工程师\n    cat > /root/.openclaw/workspaces/it/IDENTITY.md << 'EOF'\n# IT工程师 Agent\n\n- **名称**: IT工程师\n\n[571 more lines in file. Use offset=101 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773588647294}}
